{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know exactly which one was on [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He might have ordered-- he actually might have ordered this kind of exploratory laparatomy on these two females.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The SS men who did the morning appell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it happened that we had an SS man who was from the northern part of Bohemia-- Sudetenland, S-U-D-E-T-E-N-L-A-N-D-- who spoke Czech.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Beztek, B-E-Z-T-E-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or D-E-K.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "T-E-K.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And who [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] offered me [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to escape [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The reason being that he found a girl in the camp whom he fell in love with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he wanted to get her out, but he wanted to test the way first.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He explained to me that he was one of the SS-- which I met only a few of them during my stay in the camps-- who was absolutely normal.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Quite normal, human-like being, who did not yell, who didn't scream, didn't hit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He also didn't count.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He just took the count for granted, and took it with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he simply told me, if I want, so-- he cannot tell me exactly how it will be done-- but he needs either money, which he knows we don't have, or gold, which means I have to keep some of the gold teeth back so that it could be melted and he could use it as a bribe to get out.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now I was thinking for a couple of days, for he gave me about four days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said to myself, for every escapee, the rule in Auschwitz was, if somebody escapes successfully, ten people will die.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
